      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer who appreciates a solid opportunity at an accessible price. A sensible choice for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a budget-minded purchase.",
