      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of potential for the right buyer. Great for someone handy, a spare runabout, or even parts depending on what you need. If you know your way around cars, there\u2019s value here and a chance to pick up something affordable without spending a fortune. Priced to attract interest and ready for its next chapter.",
